    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 13 (Spell Level 7)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 28 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 16 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 30</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This very potent technique has been forbidden because it is a cruel weapon that can leave disturbing mental scars on its subject. Your hand flares up with blazing flames, which will deal 8d8 fire damage to the touched target. In addition, the target is marked with a blazing seal, which deals 2d6+1 fire damage each round and lasts 1d8+2 rounds. Only a successful use of the Fuuka Houin technique can remove the brand and its flames (other than its duration expiring).<br><br>Each round the brand deals damage, the target will cower for 1 round and suffer 1 temporary Wisdom damage (Will DC 16 negates both effects).</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
